Sentencas: This paper presents the work on the development of an anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC).
Titulo: Performance evaluation of anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells with thin film YSZ electrolyte

Sentencas: The cell consists of a Ni-YSZ anode as the cell support, a 45-mum thick YSZ electrolyte and a screen-printed LSM-YSZ/LSM double-layer cathode.
Titulo: Performance evaluation of anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells with thin film YSZ electrolyte

Sentencas: Effect of cell activation and operating conditions such as temperature and airflow rate on the cell performance was investigated.
Titulo: Performance evaluation of anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells with thin film YSZ electrolyte

Sentencas: We found that for a newly prepared cell, there was effective activation on electrodes by current treatment, and the improved performance of the cell was actually a consequence of cathode activation.
Titulo: Performance evaluation of anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells with thin film YSZ electrolyte

Sentencas: The maximum power density at 800degreesC of this cell with an active area of 0.5 cm(2) is 0.93 W/cm(2) with 500 ml/min of airflow rate.
Titulo: Performance evaluation of anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells with thin film YSZ electrolyte

Sentencas: The study also revealed that obtaining cell impedance data under loading provides an alternative way to assess the performance of the SOFC.
Titulo: Performance evaluation of anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells with thin film YSZ electrolyte
